Google Sheets Clone
A web-based spreadsheet application inspired by Google Sheets, built using React, Handsontable, Node.js, Express, and MongoDB. This project allows users to create, edit, and save spreadsheets with support for formulas.

🚀 Features
✅ Handsontable-based spreadsheet UI
✅ Save and load spreadsheets to/from MongoDB
✅ Supports basic formulas like SUM, AVERAGE, MAX, MIN, COUNT, etc.
✅ Text transformation functions: TRIM, UPPER, LOWER, FIND_AND_REPLACE
✅ Remove duplicate values in a range
✅ Dynamic cell calculations

🛠️ Tech Stack
Frontend: React.js, Handsontable, Axios
Backend: Node.js, Express.js, MongoDB, Mongoose
Styling: CSS
Deployment: (Optional) AWS, Vercel, or Netlify
