▶️ Start Frontend (React App)
sh
Copy
Edit
npm start
This will start the React app at http://localhost:3000.

📚 API Endpoints
Method	Endpoint	Description
POST	/save	Save a spreadsheet
GET	/load/:name	Load a spreadsheet by name
📝 Usage
1️⃣ Open the React app and start editing the spreadsheet.
2️⃣ Use formulas like:

=SUM(A1:A5)
=AVERAGE(B1:B10)
=MAX(C1:C10)
=COUNT(D1:D5)
=UPPER(A1)
=LOWER(A1)
=FIND_AND_REPLACE(A1, "old", "new")
=REMOVE_DUPLICATES(A1:A10)
3️⃣ Click the Save button to store your sheet in MongoDB.
4️⃣ Reload the page and retrieve your saved sheet.
🎯 Future Enhancements
🔹 Multi-user collaboration
🔹 Real-time updates with WebSockets
🔹 Export & Import to CSV/Excel
🔹 Advanced formula support

